<Layout 
  title="Moving Again | Interstate Removalists Australia"
  description="Moving Again is Australia's most trusted interstate removalist. Get a quote for furniture removals, car transport, and container transport today."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 mb-6 rounded-full bg-brand-red/10 text-brand-red font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm border border-brand-red/20">
        Trusted Nationwide
      </span>
      
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-brand-dark mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-tight">
        Moving Made <span class="text-brand-red">Easy.</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Professional interstate removalists, car transport, and container shipping. 
        We handle the heavy lifting so you can focus on your new beginning.
      </p>

